const_iterator begin()  const noexcept;

{{dcl | num=2 | since=c++23 |
const_iterator cbegin() const noexcept;
}}
{{dcl end}}

Returns an iterator to the first entry of the {{tt|basic_stacktrace}}. 

If the {{tt|basic_stacktrace}} is empty, the returned iterator is equal to {{lc|end()}}.

{{image|range-begin-end.svg}}

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
Iterator to the first entry.

===Complexity===
Constant.
